{"tid":1386832,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"關於coupon","createTime":"2019-07-30T12:02:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T13:45:10.000Z","uid":273512,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8257a459e0ef877e349eaf13a1df7dfee9ba73af","tid":1386832,"uid":273512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:02:50.000Z","msg":"作為一個廢中，平時都會用信用卡積分去換下超市同餐廳coupon<br />\n<br />\n今日突然諗起（唔知有冇人已經講左），我後生果時有幾可去拎coupon 買嘢？<br />\n<br />\n如果而家無啦啦有班後生仔女拎d coupon 出黎用，咁咪好似好特別囉？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以會唔會大家都得閒就用下coupon 買嘢食換嘢食，人人都用coupon, coupon 就唔會特別引人留意啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢d 事和理非同銀絲都好易做到<br />\n<br />\n咁到時師奶要去打牌唔想煮飯，畀兩張M 記卷叫個仔去換嘢食都好合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個孫幫呀婆換湯水同蒸飯都好岩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知大家點睇？"},{"pid":"5e88533ba1481976772fc70d53d66f09fdba6f4d","tid":1386832,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:04:26.000Z","msg":"好好奇話自己係廢中到底有幾中 四五十？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5425896e16491651cc309b9e5fd7e9b6f402a244","tid":1386832,"uid":273512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e88533ba1481976772fc70d53d66f09fdba6f4d","tid":1386832,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:04:26.000Z","msg":"好好奇話自己係廢中到底有幾中 四五十？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:45:10.000Z","msg":"係中央肥胖嘅中<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}